column3: When i go back to Japan I will bring my bike
Ottimo video. I video Rapha di qualche anno fa sono migliori. Sono cambiati i ciclisti o le idee di produzione dei filmati ?
These videos are tremendous. Really capture the love of cycling/life.
What make/model is the orange bike in the VT?

After visit of my sister to Tokyo last year, she came back telling me," You are gone to love it cause many people use bike to get around the city". Hope, I'll get a chance to visit this lovely city someday.
I will cycle Japan some day, it's my favourite place.Keep these coming!
